
Welcome to BlarfenBlargen!

This is a story about trials facing the Seven Deadly Sins that a duo of dwarven brothers
went through to claim back the Throne of Old from their lineage!

There are key interactions with your brother throughout the trials
as well as decisions that change the outcome towards the end of the game.

Be careful!

Your choice during some of the trials do matter!

As for which ones matter...
That is something for you to explore!

Good luck and may your beards ever stay scruffy!

Remember...

You can use the command:

----
$ cd
----

to continue on in the story.

EXAMPLE:
Type
------------------------
$ cd underground_kingdom
------------------------

Remember to cast cat journal once in...
So the story begins...

